The company Nintendo recently requested help in cracking down on piracy of
video games in countries like Mexico. _Tome Chango Su Banana_ [explains that
piracy won't stop “unless they lower their
prices”](http://www.tomechangosubanana.com/2009/piracy-in-mexico-why-it-wont-
stop) and compares prices of the console and games in his country and the
United States.

